GET {{baseUrlV1}}/health
Accept: application/json

### Listar todos los géneros
GET {{baseUrlV1}}/genres
Accept: application/json

### Crear un género
POST {{baseUrlV1}}/genres
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "name": "Suspenso",
  "description": "Películas con tensión y giros inesperados.",
  "is_active": true
}

### Ver un género
GET {{baseUrlV1}}/genres/{{genreId}}
Accept: application/json

### Actualizar un género
PUT {{baseUrlV1}}/genres/{{genreId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "name": "Suspenso Psicológico",
  "is_active": true
}

### Eliminar un género (soft delete)
DELETE {{baseUrlV1}}/genres/{{genreId}}
Accept: application/json

### Listar géneros con filtros y ordenamiento
GET {{baseUrlV1}}/genres?search=en&is_active=true&sort_by=name&order=desc
Accept: application/json

### Buscar género por slug
GET {{baseUrlV1}}/genres/slug/suspenso-psicologico
Accept: application/json

### Restaurar un género eliminado
POST {{baseUrlV1}}/genres/{{genreId}}/restore
Accept: application/json

### =============================
### PELÍCULAS
### =============================

### Listar todas las películas
GET {{baseUrlV1}}/movies
Accept: application/json

### Listar películas con filtros
GET {{baseUrlV1}}/movies?search=padrino&year=1972&min_rating=8&genre_id=4&sort_by=rating&order=desc
Accept: application/json

### Crear una película
POST {{baseUrlV1}}/movies
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "title": "Blade Runner",
  "synopsis": "Un policía caza androides en un futuro distópico.",
  "year": 1982,
  "rating": 8.1,
  "director": "Ridley Scott",
  "duration": 117,
  "genre_ids": [6]
}

### Ver una película
GET {{baseUrlV1}}/movies/{{movieId}}
Accept: application/json

### Actualizar una película
PUT {{baseUrlV1}}/movies/{{movieId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "rating": 9.0,
  "genre_ids": [4]
}

### Eliminar una película (soft delete)
DELETE {{baseUrlV1}}/movies/{{movieId}}
Accept: application/json

### =============================
### AUTENTICACIÓN (JWT)
### =============================

### Registrar un usuario
POST {{baseUrlV1}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "name": "Teddy Paz",
  "email": "teddy@movie-api.test",
  "password": "password123",
  "password_confirmation": "password123"
}

###

### Iniciar sesión
POST {{baseUrlV1}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "email": "teddy@movie-api.test",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### Ver usuario autenticado (requiere token)
GET {{baseUrlV1}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Refrescar token (renovar)
POST {{baseUrlV1}}/auth/refresh
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Cerrar sesión
POST {{baseUrlV1}}/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json


### Listar todas las películas con la versión 2
GET {{baseUrlV2}}/movies
Accept: application/json

### Ver una película con la versión 2
GET {{baseUrlV2}}/movies/{{movieId}}
Accept: application/json
